title: 12/14 Fantasy Football Podcast: Start or Sit (AFC); Stats That Matter
description:
Starting off with some Week 15 sleepers (2:00), then find out why Dak Prescott is our Start of the Week (4:35) and why Heath isn't buying in ... Stats that might matter for Kareem Hunt (14:30), Joe Flacco (17:28) and Jarvis Landry (19:12). Plus an Aizer Fantasy Tip (20:10) for the first time in a long time ...
